                <h1>Calvin Johnson: NFL Legend and Hall of Famer</h1>
                <p>Calvin Johnson, also known as "Megatron," is a former NFL wide receiver who played for the Detroit Lions. Renowned for his incredible athleticism and catching ability, he set multiple records during his career, including the single-season receiving yards record. Johnson's legacy in football is cemented by his induction into the Pro Football Hall of Fame.</p>
